metadata.description:
This is the picture that inspired the whole project.

Stone, earth, paint, people, dirt, water, light, iron, wood, air. Every hand that touches the wall, summons little creatures on it so they can live there for a little time. Those layers and textures stack up and become a playground, a life itself. 

This piece is from a wall on Urban Spree in Berlin.
